 has thrusted many other issues of massive significance onto the backburners. In fact, there has been minimal dialogue discussing one of the </span><b>biggest</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> public health problems of our time. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, before I delve into this issue, its important that I state this right from the get-go: I do not believe that it is necessary for universities to buy brand-name hygiene products and supply all of the students for their entire duration at the university. Although I would absolutely love to see such a thing happen, its important to note that this could become quite costly and discourage universities from even taking the first step at all. With that said, I do firmly believe that any and every student should have the right to access a high-quality tampon or a pad immediately if they ever need it, no matter what their gender, race, or socioeconomic standing is, whether it be due to an emergency or even affordability. The physical, social, and mental toll that people can suffer in not having access to these products right away is tremendous and by solving this issue from ever manifesting, students can avoid stress. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It has become high-time for colleges, whether it be their student government or administration, to protect the interest of their own students. Several schools have taken steps into the right direction; its now time for other schools to take up the mantle and truly ensure the health of their students. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"visibility_display\";s:0:\"\";s:26:\"visibility_user_capability\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"animation\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"animation_delay\";s:3:\"0.0\";s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"rich-text\";}}}");
